{"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Getting started","generated":true,"anchor":"Getting-started","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"1. Add the SDK","anchor":"1-Add-the-SDK"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Add the "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"YEOFR","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" Swift package"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"https:\/\/github.com\/YEOMessaging\/YEOFR-SPM"},{"type":"text","text":") to your project, pinned to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"exact version "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.5.9","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", then "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"import YEOFR"},{"type":"text","text":". The binary is "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"arm64","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"device-only","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — it does not run on the simulator."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"2. Pilot unlock for non-YEO bundle IDs","anchor":"2-Pilot-unlock-for-non-YEO-bundle-IDs"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YEOFR is gated to YEO-owned apps by default; a non-YEO bundle id aborts on"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"construction. Evaluation customers get a "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"temporary unlock code","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"bypasses the gate during a fixed pilot window — email"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"christo@yeomessaging.com","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" to request one. Pass it to the initializer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(step 3). YEO-owned apps pass the gate natively."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"3. Drive everything with `FaceTrustService`","anchor":"3-Drive-everything-with-FaceTrustService"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is the turnkey entry point. It owns the engine, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"camera, the fused-trust pipeline (face recognition + liveness CNN +"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TrueDepth), the identity gate, and tracker persistence, and exposes two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"streams: one for live trust verdicts and one for guided enrolment."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["import YEOFR","","let service = FaceTrustService(pilotUnlockCode: \"YOUR-PILOT-CODE\")","","\/\/ Attach the preview to an AVCaptureVideoPreviewLayer:","\/\/   previewLayer.session = service.previewSession","","try await service.start()    \/\/ warm-up, restore enrolment, arm gate, start camera"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"4. Enrol a face","anchor":"4-Enrol-a-face"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"enroll(name:)"},{"type":"text","text":" runs a short guided capture, persists the gallery, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"re-arms the identity gate. Iterate the returned stream to coach the user:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["for await step in service.enroll(name: \"Alice\") {","    switch step.phase {","    case .capturing: show(step.prompt, progress: step.poseProgress)","    case .completed: dismiss()","    case .failed:    show(step.prompt)","    @unknown default: break","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A single front pose is enough to separate the enrolled user from other"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"people. Pass "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"poses: PoseTarget.lightingAwareGallerySequence"},{"type":"text","text":" to also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"capture off-axis poses + a lighting pass, which improves recall as the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user turns their head."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"5. Run live recognition","anchor":"5-Run-live-recognition"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["for await update in service.updates() {","    switch update.status {","    case .trusted:    badge(\"TRUSTED — \\(update.matchedName ?? \"\")\", .green)","    case .notTrusted: badge(\"NOT TRUSTED\", .red)","    case .badFraming: badge(\"ADJUST FRAMING\", .orange)","    case .noFace:     badge(\"NO FACE\", .gray)","    @unknown default: break","    }","    \/\/ update.livenessGenuine \/ update.depthIsThreeD are the contributing signals.","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"update.status == .trusted"},{"type":"text","text":" already fuses face recognition, liveness, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TrueDepth, with framing applied — you never pick a similarity threshold,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and you never touch the identity gate (forgetting it would collapse trust"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to liveness + depth, so any live face would pass). The enrolled gallery is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"saved across launches automatically; "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"service.enrolledName"},{"type":"text","text":" reflects who is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"enrolled."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"See also","anchor":"See-also"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A complete, runnable SwiftUI app lives in the package’s "},{"code":"Examples\/FRPilot","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" — full API."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustUpdate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" \/ "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/EnrollmentProgress","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" — the stream payloads."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Recognise the enrolled user and reject everyone else, in a few lines.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"title":"QuickStart","modules":[{"name":"YEOFR"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/quickstart"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/quickstart"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"article","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/QuickStart"},"references":{"doc://com.yeomessaging.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustService/updates()":{"role":"symbol","title":"updates()","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Per-frame trust verdicts for the recognition UI. Call once and iterate;"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the stream finishes on "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"stop()"},{"type":"text","text":". Newest-wins (the underlying camera"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"stream drops stale frames), so a slow consumer can’t back up memory."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"updates","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AsyncStream","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScS"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"FaceTrustUpdate","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FaceTrustUpdateV"},{"text":">","kind":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustservice\/updates()","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/updates()"},"doc://com.yeomessaging.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"On-device face recognition with fused liveness and TrueDepth anti-spoofing.","type":"text"}],"title":"YEOFR","role":"collection"},"doc://com.yeomessaging.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustService":{"role":"symbol","title":"FaceTrustService","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"FaceTrustService"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Turnkey entry point for on-device face recognition with fused liveness","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and TrueDepth anti-spoofing.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"FaceTrustService"}],"url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustservice","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService"},"doc://com.yeomessaging.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustService/enroll(name:poses:)":{"role":"symbol","title":"enroll(name:poses:)","abstract":[{"text":"Enrol ","type":"text"},{"code":"name","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" from the live camera and return a stream of capture","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"progress. The existing frame loop drives the gallery walk; on completion","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the service persists the gallery, refreshes ","type":"text"},{"code":"enrolledName","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", resets the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"trust pipeline against the fresh gallery, and re-arms the identity gate —","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the consumer does none of that.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"enroll","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"name","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"poses","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"text":"PoseTarget","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR10PoseTargetO"},{"text":"]) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AsyncStream","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScS"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"EnrollmentProgress","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR18EnrollmentProgressV"},{"text":">","kind":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustservice\/enroll(name:poses:)","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/enroll(name:poses:)"},"doc://com.yeomessaging.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/EnrollmentProgress":{"role":"symbol","title":"EnrollmentProgress","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"EnrollmentProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Progress for an in-flight enrolment capture. Yielded by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/enroll(name:poses:)"},{"type":"text","text":" and the stream finishes once the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"gallery is banked (or the capture can’t start)."}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"EnrollmentProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/enrollmentprogress","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.yeomessaging.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/EnrollmentProgress"},"doc://com.yeomessaging.YEO